arCallbackSets.szOnSetCompleteScript:
Hydra.ActorEnableAI(ID_BOSS)
Hydra.QActorPower(ID_BOSS, POWER_SHOUT)

Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(ID_BOSS)

Hydra.ActorMergeAIState(ID_BOSS, AISTATE_STAYINARENA, ID_BOSS, 0)
Hydra.QuestAdvancePhase()

arCallbacks.szOnCallbackCompleteScript:
function Start()
	local sChest = ACTOR_CHEST_REWARD

	if Hydra.QuestGetBonusPhaseResult() then
		sChest = ACTOR_CHEST_REWARD_HEROIC
	end
	
	Events.SpawnRewardChest(CHEST_LOCATION, sChest)
end

function Start(sEventName, idActor, nUserParam)
	Hydra.ActorAddToPrefabScopedGroup(nUserParam, "LE_Empowered_Boss")
	Hydra.QuestSetCustomParamFromActor(2, nUserParam)
end

function Start(idActor, flPrevHP, flHp)
	updateChannelSpawner(ID_SPAWNER_CHANNELER_1)
	Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(ID_THIS_QUEST, EG_MINOR_WAVE)
	
	Hydra.ActorSetDamageCap(ID_BOSS, 0.59)
end

function Start(idActor, flPrevHP, flHp)
	updateChannelSpawner(ID_SPAWNER_CHANNELER_2)
	Hydra.ActorsEnableLinkedByActorInGroup(ID_THIS_QUEST, "spawnerAmbient2")
	-- Spawn elites here
	-- We do this instead of use a population because we want 1 fewer elites, since theire
	-- is a unique elite roaming already. No elites on WT1-2
	if Hydra.GameGetCurrentWorldTier() >= Hydra.WORLD_TIER_3 then
		Hydra.ActorTriggerSpawnerUpdate(ID_AMBIENT_ELITE)
		if Hydra.GameGetCurrentWorldTier() == Hydra.WORLD_TIER_4 then
			Hydra.ActorTriggerSpawnerUpdate(ID_AMBIENT_ELITE)
		end
	end
	Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(ID_THIS_QUEST, EG_MAJOR_WAVE)
	Hydra.ActorSetDamageCap(ID_BOSS, 0.29)
end

function Start(idActor, flPrevHP, flHp)
	updateChannelSpawner(ID_SPAWNER_CHANNELER_3)
	Hydra.ActorsEnableLinkedByActorInGroup(ID_THIS_QUEST, "spawnerAmbient3")
	Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(ID_THIS_QUEST, EG_MINOR_WAVE)
	Hydra.ActorSetDamageCap(ID_BOSS, 0.049)
end

function Start(idActor, flPrevHP, flHp)
	
	Hydra.ActorMergeAIState(ID_BOSS, AISTATE_TRANSFORM, ID_BOSS)
	Hydra.ActorRemoveMergedAIState(ID_BOSS, AISTATE_STAYINARENA)
	
	local bShouldWait = false

	for i, actorID in pairs(Hydra.ActorsInPrefabScopedGroup(PSAG_CHANNELERS)) do
		if Hydra.ActorIsAlive(actorID) then
			Hydra.ActorKill(actorID)
			bShouldWait = true
		end
	end
	
	if bShouldWait then
		Hydra.Wait(1.02)
	end

	updateChannelSpawner(ID_SPAWNER_CHANNELER_4)
end

arCallbackSets.szOnSetCompleteScript:
if not Hydra.QuestGetBonusPhaseResult() then
	Hydra.QuestAdvancePhase()
end

arQuestPhases.szOnExitScript:
for i, actorID in pairs(T_SPAWNERS) do
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(actorID) then
		Hydra.ActorDelete(actorID)
	end
end

Hydra.ActorKill(ID_ARENA)

for i, actorID in pairs(Hydra.ActorsInPrefabScopedGroup(PSAG_CHANNELERS)) do
	Hydra.ActorRemoveMergedAIState(actorID, AISTATE_CHANNEL)
end

arCallbacks.szOnCallbackCompleteScript:
function Start(idActorKiller, idActorKilled)

	for i, actorID in pairs(Hydra.ActorsInPrefabScopedGroup(PSAG_ALL_MOBS)) do
		Hydra.QActorWait(actorID, Hydra.GetRandomFloat(0, 0.5))
		Hydra.QActorKill(actorID)
	end
end

function Start(idActorSpawned, idActorSpawner)
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(ID_BOSS) then
		Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(idActorSpawned, EG_CHANNELER_SHOUT)
		Hydra.ActorAddAITarget(idActorSpawned, ID_BOSS, true)
		Hydra.ActorMergeAIState(idActorSpawned, AISTATE_CHANNEL, idActorSpawned, 0)
	end
end

function Start(idActorSpawned, idActorSpawner)
	ID_BOSS = idActorSpawned
	Hydra.ActorEnableAI(idActorSpawned, false)
	Hydra.BuffApplyToTarget(POWER_CHANNEL, "AI_TARGET", ID_BOSS)
	Hydra.QuestSetCustomParamFromActor(1, ID_BOSS)
	Hydra.SetActorVariable(ID_BOSS, "questID", ID_THIS_QUEST)
	Hydra.ActorSetDamageCap(ID_BOSS, 0.9)
	Events.ActorSetPhased(ID_BOSS, true)
	Hydra.BuffApplyToTarget(POWER_BOSS_MODIFIERS, "NO_LEASH", ID_BOSS)
end

arQuestPhases.szOnEnterScript:
if Hydra.ActorIsValid(ID_BOSS) then
	Hydra.ActorMergeAIState(ID_BOSS, AISTATE_DESPAWN, ID_BOSS)
	Hydra.DisplayGameMessageForAllQuestParticipants("Messages:LE_Empowered_BossEscaped")
end

szUserFunctionsScript:
local function updateChannelSpawner(idNewChannelSpawner)

	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idCurrentChannelSpawner) then
		Hydra.ActorDelete(idCurrentChannelSpawner)
	end
	
	idCurrentChannelSpawner = idNewChannelSpawner
	
	if Hydra.PrefabScopedActorGroupGetCount(PSAG_CHANNELERS) == 0 then
		Hydra.ActorEnable(idCurrentChannelSpawner)
	end
	
end
szOnStartupScript:
idCurrentChannelSpawner = Hydra.ACDID_INVALID
PSAG_CHANNELERS = "LE_Empowered_Channeler"
PSAG_ALL_MOBS = "LE_Empowered_AllMobs"
ID_THIS_QUEST = Hydra.QuestGetOwner()

updateChannelSpawner(ID_INITIAL_CHANNEL_SPAWNER)
